{"product_id":"black-basic-bottom","title":"BLACK BASIC BOTTOM","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n420 GSM TAPED COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e\nCOMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e\nSTRAIGHT BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e\nJET BLACK MINIMAL DESIGN\u003cbr\u003e\nUNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM premium taped cotton fleece for a dense, structured feel with long-term durability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette delivers relaxed comfort with a modern streetwear edge.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClean blank finish makes it easy to pair with graphic tees, hoodies, or elevated essentials.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eJet black tone offers a timeless, sharp look suitable for both casual and styled outfits.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTaped fleece construction adds structure while maintaining flexibility and everyday comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect for all seasons, offering warmth, breathability, and a premium heavyweight presence.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the bottoms inside out with similar colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric depth and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain structure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore folded in a cool, dry place to retain shape.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e420 GSM taped fleece for a substantial premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for versatile, comfortable wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex design suitable for multiple body types and styles.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMinimal blank aesthetic for effortless outfit pairing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for adjustable comfort and support.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll-season fabric balance between warmth and breathability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881408647322,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881408680090,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881408712858,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881408745626,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881408778394,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881408811162,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00478copy_1__11zon.jpg?v=1772290631","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/black-basic-bottom","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}